s","guid":"M6TBAaXKjYuxnBNEGgXQLQ","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"AntiTPO","guid":"M6nNMv2VYnIAo9jP4yOBIw","children":[{"id":"34","parent":"33","text":"Presente en el 90 % al 95 % de los pacientes","guid":"0oAYTlyw6cPFn2iIeyXfyg","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"33","text":"Si está presente, no es necesario realizar más pruebas de anticuerpos","guid":"YBDKxtKP1eyK2S1-iANyCg","children":[]}]},{"id":"36","parent":"32","text":"Anticuerpos contra la tiroglobulina\\N(TgAb)","guid":"VpX75cNPqGCo75ItQps4bQ","children":[{"id":"37","parent":"36","text":"Presentes en el 60 % al 80 % de los pacientes","guid":"cWchDgNrsGmBsSvsTzI0vA","children":[]}]},{"id":"38","parent":"32","text":"Anticuerpos antirreceptor de TSH","guid":"4pJUuOl86lmgcpW8qyIg1w","children":[{"id":"39","parent":"38","text":"Presentes en aproximadamente el 10 % de los pacientes","guid":"xlstD7AKLrj65qVYQQmIUw","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"40","parent":"24","text":"Por lo general, no se indican más pruebas a menos que se sospeche de malignidad.","guid":"TUDbXjF9ZdwFCZ2lRNtRjw","children":[]}]},{"id":"41","parent":"23","text":"Ecografía de\\Nla tiroides","guid":"PydDAhMFeq6RZOi13D5kyA","children":[{"id":"42","parent":"41","text":"Nódulo palpable","guid":"oXTot2YlY1VD7mC_mVzTfA","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"41","text":"Bocio multinodular","guid":"oOdTsu8uhyh_55W0_MHIyg","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"41","text":"Bocio asociado con la adenopatía cervical","guid":"1f1Y6sYGPsGfG6mInu_WZA","children":[]}]},{"id":"45","parent":"23","text":"Aspiración de\\Naguja fina","guid":"F4h6OQbziN9PtcXnJzDVng","children":[{"id":"46","parent":"45","text":"Nódulo tiroideo sospechoso\\No de rápido crecimiento.","guid":"BtYhjYGzzibQGcyThxlw8g","children":[{"id":"47","parent":"46","text":"≤ 1 cm ","guid":"nLj-b58hOr2SE3o48duf1w","children":[{"id":"48","parent":"47","text":"No se recomienda la biopsia de FNA","guid":"xly5UF2zpcyZyR4r_q0c4w","children":[]}]},{"id":"49","parent":"46","text":"≥ 1 cm","guid":"jb4